		<h2>Summary:</h2><div class="t"><div class="b"><div class="l"><div class="r"><div class="bl"><div class="br"><div class="tl"><div class="tr"><img src="/civilopedia/images/peace.png" alt="peace" /> Faith is the currency which enables you to found a Pantheon, makes Great Prophets spawn and can be used to purchase religious units and buildings.<br /><br />There are several sources for <img src="/civilopedia/images/peace.png" alt="peace" /> Faith points. There are buildings or wonders that award a certain amount of <img src="/civilopedia/images/peace.png" alt="peace" /> Faith per round if you build them in your cities. Some Natural Wonders can also generate it when they are being worked. You can find <img src="/civilopedia/images/peace.png" alt="peace" /> Faith in Ancient Ruins. If you befriend a religious city-state they will also contribute with regular gifts. And the last source of <img src="/civilopedia/images/peace.png" alt="peace" /> Faith is the tile improvement Holy Site that Great Prophets can erect on your lands.</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
